  "time_ut": 1660749560,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dc4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd - \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0dad\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Polgahawela-Colombo train has also stopped after running into a bedroom",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Transport says that the office train that runs daily from Polgahawela to Colombo Fort has been suspended for about a week due to a sleeping room problem for the train drivers.",
        "The Ministry of Transport said that among the drivers' bedrooms at the Polgahawela station is the bedroom of the driver of the Polgahawela-Colombo train number 528 and the driver of the Kandy-Polgahawela train has left the train due to his objection to allowing the driver of the Kandy-Polgahawela train to sleep in that room.",
        "The Ministry of Transport also says that the driver has to pay an overtime allowance of 18 hours a day even though he has left the train causing inconvenience to a large number of passengers.",
        "The Ministry of Transport said that thousands of commuters traveling to their offices daily by train are facing a difficult situation due to the shortage of drivers in the Railway Department."
      ],
